column5: Anyone have a Rice Lake report? Planning on renting a boat tomorrow.  Just curious how the weekend went.
Try the Rice Lake Fishing Board or the Kawartha Anglers Board.  Usually reports on there.  Cheers.
So, how'd ya make out?  I did well there on thursday for eyes.  S.
I was out yesterday out of bewdley.... Hit 11 fish between 6-11am all on stick baits .... Get on those weed egdes !!!
It was great... rented a boat out of Gores landing.  We hit about 15 eyes along the weed lines.  Great day on the waters!!!
